sql: SELECT Products.product_id FROM Products JOIN Order_Items ON Order_Items.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Order_Items WHERE Products.product_id = product_id)
SELECT order_id, product_id FROM Order_Items WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND item_status_code > (SELECT SUM(item_status_code) FROM Order_Items AS h WHERE h.order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10)

SELECT product_category, product_name FROM Products WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR product_id NOT IN (SELECT product_id FROM Order_Items WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10) GROUP BY product_name LIMIT 5
SELECT customer_id FROM Customer_Orders WHERE order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY customer_id DESC
SELECT SUM(product_id), COUNT(DISTINCT product_category), product_category FROM Products WHERE  product_id >= 44
SELECT COUNT(Order_Items.order_id), COUNT(DISTINCT shipping_method_code) FROM Customer_Orders JOIN Order_Items ON Customer_Orders.order_id = Order_Items.order_id WHERE  product_id <= 25 LIMIT 6
SELECT u.product_id, u.product_category FROM Products AS u WHERE u.product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  u.product_id != 49

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT item_id), order_item_status_code FROM Products JOIN Order_Items ON Order_Items.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE product_id NOT IN (SELECT product_id FROM Products WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10) LIMIT 2
SELECT product_id, product_id FROM Products WHERE  product_id <= 64 LIMIT 5
SELECT product_id, product_name FROM Products WHERE  product_id < 29 ORDER BY product_name ASC LIMIT 7
SELECT customer_id, customer_id FROM Customer_Orders

SELECT COUNT(Premises.premise_id), Premises.premise_details FROM Premises AS b JOIN Premises ON Premises.premise_id = b.premise_id WHERE  b.premise_id = 0 GROUP BY Premises.premise_details HAVING MIN(b.premise_id) <= 56
SELECT COUNT(l.premise_id), l.premises_type FROM Premises AS l WHERE l.premise_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 1
SELECT AVG(Customers.customer_id), Mailshot_Customers.customer_id FROM Mailshot_Customers JOIN Customers ON Customers.customer_id = Mailshot_Customers.customer_id WHERE  mailshot_id < 72 LIMIT 8
SELECT SUM(i.mailshot_id), COUNT(DISTINCT i.mailshot_id), i.mailshot_name FROM Mailshot_Campaigns AS i WHERE  i.mailshot_id <= 68 GROUP BY i.mailshot_name ORDER BY i.mailshot_name ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT w.premise_id), w.customer_id, w.date_address_to FROM Customer_Addresses AS w WHERE  w.premise_id < 47 GROUP BY w.date_address_to ORDER BY w.customer_id ASC
SELECT AVG(z.premise_id), MAX(z.customer_id), z.premise_id, z.address_type_code FROM Customer_Addresses AS z WHERE  z.customer_id = 73 GROUP BY z.address_type_code HAVING COUNT(z.premise_id) = 82
SELECT product_id FROM Products WHERE product_name NOT IN (SELECT product_name FROM Products AS g)
SELECT e.mailshot_id, e.customer_id FROM Mailshot_Customers AS e WHERE e.mailshot_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  e.mailshot_id != 55 ORDER BY e.mailshot_id ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT e.product_id), e.product_id, e.product_category FROM Products AS e WHERE  e.product_id < 62 AND product_name IN (SELECT product_name FROM Products WHERE  product_id < 49 LIMIT 9) GROUP BY e.product_category HAVING AVG(e.product_id) < 42 ORDER BY e.product_id DESC LIMIT 10

SELECT AVG(Order_Items.order_id), order_item_status_code, item_order_quantity FROM Customer_Orders JOIN Order_Items ON Customer_Orders.order_id = Order_Items.order_id WHERE Order_Items.order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  customer_id = 70 LIMIT 4
SELECT customer_id, outcome_code, outcome_code FROM Mailshot_Customers WHERE  customer_id > 36
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT payment_method) FROM Customers WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR customer_name IN (SELECT customer_name FROM Customers AS e WHERE  e.customer_id <= 38)

SELECT SUM(mailshot_id), mailshot_id FROM Mailshot_Customers JOIN Customers ON Customers.customer_id = Mailshot_Customers.customer_id WHERE  mailshot_id = 62 AND customer_name IN (SELECT customer_name FROM Customers LIMIT 1) ORDER BY mailshot_id ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT premise_id), COUNT(DISTINCT premise_id), premise_id FROM Premises WHERE  premise_id = 12 ORDER BY premise_id DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT payment_method), customer_id FROM Customers WHERE  customer_id >= 18 LIMIT 5
SELECT product_name, product_name, product_category FROM Products GROUP BY product_category
